data.description: $10,000 Price Reduction!  This all brick cape cod is very spacious and offers 5 bedrooms, 2 full baths, a finished basement, screened in porch off the kitchen, plenty of room in the back yard for the kids to play, a deck and a covered front porch.  New in the last 2 years are the HVAC, windows, upstairs flooring, toilet and sink in the upstairs bathroom and built in microwave.  You will also love the beautiful flooring throughout, the kitchen with stainless appliances and the finished basement with a large open area and a bedroom. 2023-11-11
